commit.message:
Replace `Haml::AttributeBuilder::BOOLEAN_ATTRIBUTES` in REFERENCE.md

The `Haml::AttributeBuilder::BOOLEAN_ATTRIBUTES` was replaced with
`Haml::BOOLEAN_ATTRIBUTES` in cb9cc050.

This commit fixes REFERENCE.md to keep the documentation up-to-date.

Provide a 'Changelog' link on rubygems.org/gems/haml

By providing a 'changelog_uri' in the metadata of the gemspec
a 'Changelog' link will be shown on https://rubygems.org/gems/haml
which makes it quick and easy for someone to check on the changes
introduced with a new version.

Details of this functionality can be found on https://guides.rubygems.org/specification-reference/

Haml 6+ is not really relevant

This applies to all versions but v6.1.3 - v6.2.5.

Fix running tests against Rails 7.1

view_paths is no longer mutable

Remove advice to run `git submodule update --init`

Hasn't been relevant since 11bb81149f4b048fe9282ed9be0dd10bfbc710b2
